high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the stove
Pick up a spoon from the table
Move to the stove behind you
Put the spoon in a pot on the stove
Pick up the pot from the stove
Move to the table behind you
Put the pot of the table
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spoon on the table in front of the stove.

high_descs: Go straight and then turn left to find the white table.
Pick up the spoon from behind the bowl on the white table.
Take the spoon and turn around to the stove.
Place the spoon in the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot and spoon from the stove.
Hold the pot and turn around to go back to the white table.
Place the pot and spoon close to the front of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Place a spoon in a pot and put them both on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the table.
Pick up the spoon from the table.
Turn around and face the stove.
Put the spoon in the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot and spoon from the stove.
Turn around towards the table.
Set the pot and spoon on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the spoon in the pot and back on the table.
